                     <interp inst="t17881022-72-person625" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , Esq; sworn.</p>
               <p>How did he behave since he has been with you? - I have heard no particular account of his behaviour.</p>
               <p>Owen. Since he has been with us, he has been very quiet; I never took any notice of any thing of the kind.</p>
